Package: pistomp-usb-automount
Version: 1.0.0-1
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: arm64
Maintainer: pistomp <pistomp@example.com>
Description: Lightweight udev-based USB automount for pi-Stomp
 Mounts USB mass-storage partitions under /media/<label> (falling back to
 /media/<kernel-dev>) on insertion, and unmounts them on removal. Replaces
 udisks2/usbmount; used by pi-Stomp to discover USB content storage
 (backups, LV2 plugins, NAM models).
